        {
            "title": "亞洲外匯市場變動不大,交易員靜待美國對伊朗採取軍事行動",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aqnZTQgQkwKU6Xox.VBcUg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEE0A0MX_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 週二,大多數亞洲貨幣和美元變動不大,投資者在美國可能對伊朗採取軍事行動的最後期限臨近之際保持謹慎態度。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元指數在亞洲交易時段上漲0.1%。截至美國東部時間02:05(格林威治標準時間06:05),美元指數期貨也上漲0.1%。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>特朗普對伊朗的最後期限迫在眉睫</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場正在倒數計時,等待總統唐納德·特朗普設定的美國東部時間晚上8:00最後期限,要求伊朗重新開放霍爾木茲海峽,此前伊朗拒絕了美國支持的停火提議。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a5814239-4cca-314d-aef6-9cc31d9a64a7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特朗普警告可能會對伊朗基礎設施發動襲擊,威脅稱\"整個國家可以在一夜之間被摧毀\"。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著緊張局勢沒有緩和跡象,投資者情緒依然脆弱。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"我們持續的評估是,鑑於這場戰爭中不同各方的期望存在巨大差距,通往和平的道路狹窄且不太可能實現,\"三菱日聯金融集團分析師在一份報告中表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日圓兌美元USD/JPY貨幣對持平交易,而韓元兌美元USD/KRW下跌0.3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">人民幣在岸匯率USD/CNY小幅下跌0.1%,而新加坡元兌美元USD/SGD基本持平。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>印度盧比在印度央行決議前走弱</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印度盧比兌美元USD/INR貨幣對上漲0.3%,投資者正在等待印度儲備銀行的利率決議,該決議將於週三公佈。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印度盧比上週走強,受到印度儲備銀行最近採取的遏制投機性持倉措施的支持,儘管地緣政治風險和原油價格高企限制了漲幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另外,澳元兌美元AUD/USD貨幣對變動不大。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者還在等待美國3月消費者物價指數(CPI)報告,該報告定於週五發佈,預計將顯示顯著上升,主要受中東衝突導致的燃料成本上漲推動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"週五的3月CPI數據可能顯示,由於汽油價格上漲,年度整體通脹率將從2.4%躍升至3.4%,但90分鐘後發佈的密歇根大學(UoM)消費者信心報告將同樣重要,\"荷蘭國際集團分析師在一份報告中表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AF%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E8%AE%8A%E5%8B%95%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%A7-%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%93%A1%E9%9D%9C%E5%BE%85%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8D%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%8E%A1%E5%8F%96%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%8B%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95-072549421.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-07 15:50:17",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "威剛3月營收破百億元續創高 Q2合約價至少再漲4成",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jEHqsNLTk9I95LLjho3FnQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/945e28812e61094b3e2938a1961d7b86\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A8%81%E5%89%9B3%E6%9C%88%E7%87%9F%E6%94%B6%E7%A0%B4%E7%99%BE%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E7%BA%8C%E5%89%B5%E9%AB%98-q2%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84%E5%83%B9%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91%E5%86%8D%E6%BC%B24%E6%88%90-070425179.html",
